{"tid":2234301,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"點解鼻哥叫做鼻哥","createTime":"2020-10-07T19:44:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T07:09:57.000Z","uid":141639,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b42c1f46e564a53d5881619c8619f1a1c432bd58","tid":2234301,"uid":141639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:44:59.000Z","msg":"即係呢個問題纏繞左我成晚<br />\n隻耳可以叫做耳仔<br />\n個嘴可以叫做嘴仔<br />\n隻眼可以叫做眼仔<br />\n點解個鼻係啊哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"366772781099e48d8a04d2fd838aea1de41b5f4b","tid":2234301,"uid":22694,"like":13,"dislike":14,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:46:42.000Z","msg":"答案係!! 陳國邦 (李斯) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為叫鼻做鼻仔係癡線 冇可能會發生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSilly發音就係 see Li 斯李<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而我地華人社會 習慣將last name 擺前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!! 答案就係李斯喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而做過李斯嘅TVB藝員就係得陳國邦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以!!!!!!!!!!!!!答案係!!!!!!!!!陳國邦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n輕鬆 謝謝大家"},{"pid":"af4dd463351c0272c743650eaaf873e2091a6a68","tid":2234301,"uid":186431,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:47:03.000Z","msg":"哥字兩個loan"},{"pid":"805624a50b0b977fc66c9508fd5651139993d247","tid":2234301,"uid":368868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:48:57.000Z","msg":"你真係好幽默"},{"pid":"7e10867f17f9610a7802bcdebb3143c5a2e192f0","tid":2234301,"uid":90820,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:50:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講開又講，廣東人叫鼻子做「鼻哥」。有說「鼻哥」由「鼻窩」音變而來：<br />\n窩/wo1；變聲母&rarr;哥/go1<br />\n其實「鼻窩」指「鼻翼」旁凹下的部分；那究竟「鼻哥」是怎樣來的呢？筆者有兩個理解：<br />\n其一、「膝蓋」，俗稱「膝頭」，是大腿與小腿相連處的外部關節。廣東人叫這部位做「膝頭哥」， 其中「哥」由「蓋」音變而來：<br />\n蓋/goi3；變調&rarr;該/goi1；變韻母&rarr;哥/go1<br />\n據此，「鼻哥」演化自「鼻蓋」--「鼻」的外面以皮膚覆「蓋」而成。<br />\n其二、首個孩子俗稱為「鼻子」，之後所生叫「鼻子」做「哥」，所以「鼻子」有「鼻哥」這俗稱。<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n文匯報<br />\n唔留link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9538cde576a5f192f028cfd8e664af936baf540d","tid":2234301,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T21:38:35.000Z","msg":"膝頭哥同鼻哥邊個大？"},{"pid":"ddf970d8b27a38bee371e95b47bf59a7394c5c1d","tid":2234301,"uid":6532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"用石頭出糧<br />\n唔會用電話, 直接行去同事度講<br />\n開會係夜晚圍住火堆開會<br />\n冇服裝要求, 男既得條褲, 女既好少少, 遮埋個胸, 人人都都赤腳"},{"pid":"3d661789caddabe9bf2cfb37ac6d7be8534c7cba","tid":2234301,"uid":247048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9538cde576a5f192f028cfd8e664af936baf540d","tid":2234301,"uid":27416,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T21:38:35.000Z","msg":"膝頭哥同鼻哥邊個大？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T23:36:30.000Z","msg":"膝頭哥食得辣椒醬，鼻哥唔得<br />\n所以膝頭哥大<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9b22dc71822555080771732bdf779150375e98c","tid":2234301,"uid":121247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddf970d8b27a38bee371e95b47bf59a7394c5c1d","tid":2234301,"uid":6532,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T21:55:07.000Z","msg":"用石頭出糧<br />\n唔會用電話, 直接行去同事度講<br />\n開會係夜晚圍住火堆開會<br />\n冇服裝要求, 男既得條褲, 女既好少少, 遮埋個胸, 人人都都赤腳"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-08T00:14:30.000Z","msg":"你讀恒管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82792bda08b2d58c2d1929dfa90c3fae18909b14","tid":2234301,"uid":367919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b42c1f46e564a53d5881619c8619f1a1c432bd58","tid":2234301,"uid":141639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-07T19:44:59.000Z","msg"